OL,5, The government has announced how all   
OL,6, households in England, Scotland and    
OL,7, Wales will receive #400 to help with   
OL,8, rising fuel bills this autumn.         
OL,10,FThe money, part of the Energy Bill     
OL,11,FSupport Scheme, will be paid in six    
OL,12,Finstalments.                           
OL,14,FHouseholds will see a discount of #66  
OL,15,Fapplied to their energy bills in       
OL,16,FOctober and November, rising to #67 a  
OL,17,Fmonth from December to March 2023.     
OL,19,FBut how the money is received will     
OL,20,Fdepend on how you pay your bill.       
